# Phase 14a.2 — file kept empty intentionally.
#
# On Cloudflare Workers Static Assets, html_handling strips the .html
# extension automatically, so the redirects in this file were creating
# an infinite loop (ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS on /home).
#
# Workers gives us these URLs natively from the file names:
#   /home              → home.html
#   /nishi-chatbot     → nishi-chatbot.html
#   /discovery-studio  → discovery-studio.html
#   /architecture-studio → architecture-studio.html
#   /program-governance → program-governance.html
#   /questionnaire     → questionnaire.html
#   /operations        → operations.html
#   /feature-explainer → feature-explainer.html
#
# If you want short aliases (/nishi, /discovery, etc.) we can add
# them later via a wrangler.jsonc routes config — but the friendly
# URLs above are enough for Phase 14a.
